---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Call from "../components/Call.astro";
const pageTitle = "About";
const description = "Discover Newark Tyres - Your trusted mobile tyre fitting experts dedicated to delivering unparalleled convenience with same-day, 7-day, and out-of-hours services. Learn more about our mission and commitment to keeping you on the move effortlessly.";
---

<MainLayout pageTitle={pageTitle} description={description}>
    <Heading mainHeading="About"/>
    <main class="container py-5">
        <p>At Newark Tyres, we're not just in the business of fitting tyres; we're in the business of fitting convenience into your life. We understand that a flat tyre can be an unexpected and frustrating disruption to your day. That's why we've dedicated ourselves to providing a mobile tyre fitting service that's as convenient as it is efficient.</p>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is simple but vital: to keep you moving. We know that your time is precious, and we don't want you to waste it waiting in a tyre shop or dealing with the stress of a flat tyre. Newark Tyres is here to ensure that tyre replacements are no longer a hassle but a seamless, hassle-free experience.</p>
        <h2>Why Choose Newark Tyres</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Same-Day Fitting:</strong> When you need a tyre replacement, you need it now. We offer same-day fitting services, so you can get back on the road without unnecessary delays.</li>
            <li><strong>7-Day Service:</strong> We operate six days a week, ensuring that you have access to our mobile tyre fitting services whenever you need them.</li>
            <li><strong>Out-of-Hours Availability:</strong> A flat tyre can happen at any moment, which is why we offer an out-of-hours callout service in case you need an emergency tyre replacement.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <p>Our team of skilled technicians is the backbone of Newark Tyres. They're not just experts in their field; they're dedicated professionals who take pride in their work. When you choose Newark Tyres, you're choosing a team committed to your safety and satisfaction.</p>
